{"seriesId":109005,"title":"RAY THE ANIMATION","thumbnailUrl":"https://nicovideo.cdn.nimg.jp/thumbnails/36423190/36423190.31432874","descriptionFirst":"零は病院に勤務することになったある夜、事故に出くわし、そこで沢病院の看護婦である美里と出会う。患部も見ずに的確な処置をする零に驚く美里。零はブラック・ジャックと名乗る謎の無免許医に移植された｢透視能力を持つ眼｣を使う天才外科医なのだ。零が沢病院へ来た早々、麻薬密売組織の一員であるという重症患者が運び込まれた。臨床実験もしていない新薬を使わないとこの男は救えない。男の口封じの為に麻薬密売組織も動き出した。沢院長は零に手術の依頼をする…。\n\n© 2005 吉富昭仁・秋田書店/RAY PROJECT\n\n次話→so36423191","tags":["ホラー/サスペンス/推理","2006年春アニメ","O.L.M","RAY"],"cours":"2006-春","colKey":"ら","relatedSeries":[],"episodes":[{"contentId":"so36423190","episodeNo":1,"title":"RAY THE ANIMATION　第1話　｢神の目｣","viewCounter":626,"commentCounter":12,"mylistCounter":26,"lengthSeconds":1451,"startTime":"2020-03-13T10:00:00+09:00","thumbnailUrl":"https://nicovideo.cdn.nimg.jp/thumbnails/36423190/36423190.31432874"},{"contentId":"so36423192","episodeNo":3,"title":"RAY THE ANIMATION　第3話　｢ガラス越しの風景｣","viewCounter":109,"commentCounter":4,"mylistCounter":0,"lengthSeconds":1451,"startTime":"2020-03-13T10:00:00+09:00","thumbnailUrl":"https://nicovideo.cdn.nimg.jp/thumbnails/36423192/36423192.88152410"},{"contentId":"so36423193","episodeNo":4,"title":"RAY THE ANIMATION　第4話　｢赤いリボン｣","viewCounter":84,"commentCounter":3,"mylistCounter":0,"lengthSeconds":1452,"startTime":"2020-03-13T10:00:00+09:00","thumbnailUrl":"https://nicovideo.cdn.nimg.jp/thumbnails/36423193/36423193.79879381"},{"contentId":"so36423194","episodeNo":5,"title":"RAY THE ANIMATION　第5話　｢成り代わり｣","viewCounter":103,"commentCounter":1,"mylistCounter":0,"lengthSeconds":1452,"startTime":"2020-03-13T10:00:00+09:00","thumbnailUrl":"https://nicovideo.cdn.nimg.jp/thumbnails/36423194/36423194.51585882"},{"contentId":"so36423197","episodeNo":8,"title":"RAY THE ANIMATION　第8話　｢蠢く過去｣","viewCounter":83,"commentCounter":3,"mylistCounter":0,"lengthSeconds":1452,"startTime":"2020-03-13T10:00:00+09:00","thumbnailUrl":"https://nicovideo.cdn.nimg.jp/thumbnails/36423197/36423197.74807818"},{"contentId":"so36423199","episodeNo":10,"title":"RAY THE